* Rage felt her prey bite into her jaw but the rumble in her stomach was 
louder then the snarls of her meal!
She bit down even harder on her prey and began to shake her head from side 
to side like that of a shark, she was hungry and wanted to eat...NOW!
Suddenly Rage felt her shoulder flair up in pain as the second raptor 
attacked her side, she moved and swayed in order to dislodge the second 
beast but it was no use!
She then decided to ignore it and turned her attentions back to the reptile 
in her mouth, her mouth watered!*
